release.body:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 4.1.x -->

## What's Changed
### Bug Fixes 🐞
* Fix logging with logger.config and no levels by @timyates in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9859
### Dependency Upgrade 🚀
* Upgraded logback to 1.4.11 by @msupic in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9857
### Tests ✅
* test: GraalVM logging by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9858

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/compare/v4.1.4...v4.1.5
release.name: Micronaut Core 4.1.5
